task.summary: Fixed extra newlines in stored content
Added delay for message passing between chain items Logging changes
Removed queue object spam from log output
Threshold support and better error prints
Fixed regex for JSON text. Clean thinking blocks before generating questions. Checks for some non-empty replies. More descriptive logging.
Change to queue-based, persistent reply and request storage
ListenerRegion now opens a readout window, unless given a different process
Clarified listener-GUI termination behavior and fixed stop/start verification logic
Fixed trying to check outboxes for regions without one
Do not look for task descriptions on ListenerRegions
Added literary critique demo gif and updated demo descriptions
Handle queue is closed before sentinel value is passed
Refactored LLM calls int a single method. Added summarize_replies()
Support for summarize_replies() and clear_replies() with Region. Remove forward() and verify() methods from visibility with ListenerRegion, as these are primarily internal.
Added docstrings for reply buffer management functions.
Added docstrings for reply buffer management functions and corrected dictionary handling logic.
Resolved timeout issue with longer LLM generation steps
Fixed some warnings and noted others.
